{"tid":668021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2018年05月17日   今日焦點‧即聽","createTime":"2018-05-17T08:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T08:50:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f6d66563b88ba23abf4e3463cc34feb99d0e57","tid":668021,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:50:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180517/20392932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180517%2F20392932&d=j%2Fc0ea5WgjbMERNZizTXtMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=7d3da181\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180517%2F20392932&h=fa186289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180517/20392932</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月17日 <br />\n<br />\n今日焦點‧即聽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要聞<br />\n‧now記者京採訪被打<br />\n‧中醫導師有非禮案底<br />\n‧般咸道兩棵大樹要斬<br />\n‧小巴超載塞多六個人<br />\n<br />\n兩岸國際<br />\n‧綠營柯P分道揚鑣<br />\n‧澳洲超市新「限奶令」<br />\n‧大馬民主象徵獲特赦<br />\n‧北韓威脅退出特金會<br />\n<br />\n評論<br />\n‧盧峯〈蘋論〉<br />\n‧李怡〈世道人生〉<br />\n‧魏仲甫論港青北上<br />\n‧林忌論港青北上<br />\n<br />\n財經<br />\n‧騰訊首季純利增六成<br />\n‧金管局再度接錢<br />\n‧沽空機構瞄準一港股<br />\n‧趙式浩大談劏廠經<br />\n<br />\n體育<br />\n‧英格蘭點兵赫特冇份<br />\n‧看台突倒塌嚇死小白<br />\n‧華杜斯可成四料得主<br />\n<br />\n娛樂<br />\n‧李宗盛第三度結婚<br />\n‧安志杰宣佈JC陀仔<br />\n‧桐谷美玲傳嫁三浦<br />\n<br />\n果籽<br />\n‧法式酒館平嘆南法菜<br />\n‧移民台灣搬屋貼士<br />\n‧藝術拼畫賀仙姐大壽"}]}